-- IBK Said to Hire StanChart to Arrange Bond Investor Meetings
-- B y   T a e j i n   P a r k
-- 2012-02-21T00:01:15Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-02-21/ibk-said-to-hire-stanchart-to-arrange-bond-investor-meetings.html
Industrial Bank of Korea (024110)  hired
Standard Chartered Plc to arrange meetings with bond investors
in  Thailand  as soon as this week, according to a person familiar
with the matter.  IBK may seek to sell bonds denominated in baht after the
talks, the person said, asking not to be named as the details
are private.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Taejin Park in Seoul at 
 tpark31@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Sarah McDonald at 
 smcdonald23@bloomberg.net  